DESCRIPTION:To join the event\, log into the digital platform\, select the relevant module (Module 1: Adaptability and Resilience)\, and navigate to the corresponding live event. You may also access the event by clicking the link in the calendar block\, which will direct you to the digital platform.\n\nThe Zoom link will become available 15 minutes before the start time. To enter the event\, go to the live event section\, click "Open\," then select the blue "Join Event" button. Please complete the registration using your professional email address.\n\nHaving trouble accessing the event via the Join Event button? No problem. Go to the live event section\, click "Open\," and copy the meeting ID and passcode listed in the event title. Be sure to complete registration using your professional email address.
